<h2
  style="
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 33px;
    letter-spacing: 0em;
    text-align: left;
  "
>
  Welcome, <%= firstName %>!
</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 32px">
  You're almost ready to get started. Next step is to verify your account. Just
  click the button below ( Link valid for 20 minutes) to verify the email
  address for your account:
</p>
<div
  style="
    background: #2585c1;
    display: inline-block;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
    width: 151px;
    padding: 8px 16px 8px 16px;
  "
>
  <a
    style="
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      line-height: 22px;
    "
    href="<%= url %>"
    >Verify email</a
  >
</div>
<p style="margin-bottom: 25px">
  If you have any trouble, try pasting this link in your browser:
  <a style="color: #00acc4; word-wrap: break-word" href="<%= url %>"
    ><%= url %></a
  >
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 5px">Best Regards</p>
